headline: Needham names Stryker top pick for 2025 on new products, margin gains
summary: Investing.com -- Needham analyst named Stryker Corporation (NYSE:SYK) its top pick for 2025, highlighting growth potential from new products, margin improvements, and expected M&A activity. Raised its price target on the stock to $442 from $409.
